{"tid":1559770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登繼續比熱青城班共諜滲透，就會影響到成個時代革命","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:23:23.000Z","uid":188176,"like":37,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"00d62ea68a783309be9c9ba5497ffce4029adf19","tid":1559770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"熱青城一直以黎，只會不斷破壞同騎劫<br />\n從來都係破壞多過貢獻<br />\n耍小聰明耍到出反效果<br />\n屌人屌到成件事散晒<br />\n永遠活係以前既幻想當中<br />\n以前既高登就係好例子<br />\n見到熱青城班撚樣又想係連登搞多次<br />\n唔該admin做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好同我講不分化，熱青城從來唔係同路人</span>"},{"pid":"42a53dec6483888d402c2e7c67fdd13dc2dacded","tid":1559770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906be6da940c94ec9f7c0f40951cce28b24a24a","tid":1559770,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"咁多熱狗，返去高登先<br />\n<br />\n但我比撚祖信BAM左"},{"pid":"b40c3f4f26e4df6dbfcddf25a47a58605011524c","tid":1559770,"uid":34223,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"記住 凡係自己唔同意嘅嘢 老屈咗佢係熱狗先 依招萬試萬靈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1b50b3b5b8e2eb28454875a18a27dd2fd0d3a1","tid":1559770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d906be6da940c94ec9f7c0f40951cce28b24a24a","tid":1559770,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"咁多熱狗，返去高登先<br />\n<br />\n但我比撚祖信BAM左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"高登熱青城大本營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f464c7a39f501877278851cbad33f21e0e4c48","tid":1559770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4